      <title>Tempo 称普拉博沃正在考虑取消印尼 3% 的赤字上限</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/prabowo-said-to-consider-removing-3-deficit-ceiling-tempo-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据当地新闻媒体 Tempo 报道，候任总统普拉博沃·苏比安托的团队正考虑取消印尼预算赤字的法律限制，因为新政府正在寻求更大的支出空间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/prabowo-said-to-consider-removing-3-deficit-ceiling-tempo-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 07:42:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
