      <title>匈牙利 CPI 跌幅超过预期，加息预期增强</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/hungary-s-inflation-dips-more-than-expected-within-target-range</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利 6 月份通胀率已从央行容忍范围上限回落，央行在即将召开的会议上考虑降息的可能性增加。匈牙利福林走弱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/hungary-s-inflation-dips-more-than-expected-within-target-range</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 06:37:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>如果 Ofwat 拒绝该计划，泰晤士水务公司将面临现金耗尽的风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/thames-water-debt-climbs-9-2-with-new-equity-raise-needed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果监管机构拒绝其 200 亿英镑（256 亿美元）的支出计划（导致客户账单增加），英国最大的供水和污水处理服务供应商明年可能会出现资金短缺。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/thames-water-debt-climbs-9-2-with-new-equity-raise-needed</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 06:20:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>穆迪下调肯尼亚评级，因致命抗议活动破坏税收计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/moody-s-cuts-kenya-ratings-after-deadly-protests-wreck-tax-plans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[肯尼亚爆发致命抗议活动，迫使政府放弃增加 20 多亿美元新税的计划，穆迪评级将肯尼亚信用评级进一步下调至垃圾级。这个东非国家的美元债券走弱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/moody-s-cuts-kenya-ratings-after-deadly-protests-wreck-tax-plans</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 05:55:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>全球银行是印度债券市场最大的多头</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/global-banks-are-the-biggest-bulls-in-india-s-bond-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[近几周，由于印度的经济前景和稳定的货币吸引，外国银行已成为印度万亿美元主权债券市场的最大投资者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/global-banks-are-the-biggest-bulls-in-india-s-bond-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 01:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本央行在最终确定债券购买削减之前试探市场参与者的意见</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/boj-sounds-out-market-players-before-finalizing-bond-buying-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本央行开始向市场参与者征询意见，了解其应以多大幅度削减债券购买规模，并计划在本月底最终确定其计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/boj-sounds-out-market-players-before-finalizing-bond-buying-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 00:15:00 GMT</pubDate>
